milestones.description: Dennis Amiss has become the top scorer in ODIs with 322 runs, going past Ian Chappell's 316
Tony Greig has conceded the most runs in an innings (63) in ODIs for ENG, going past Bob Willis's record of 55
England's 266 is the highest total in ODIs, surpassing Australia's 265
John Edrich and Fletcher's 83-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 41 between Dennis Amiss and Hampshire
Alan Knott and Tony Greig's 42-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 35 between Fletcher and Chris Old
